    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛筹集 210 亿美元建立其最大私人信贷池</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/goldman-racks-up-21-billion-for-its-largest-private-credit-pool</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团已为私人信贷投资筹集了 210 亿美元，这是该集团迄今为止为华尔街最热门的资产类别投入的最大一笔资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/goldman-racks-up-21-billion-for-its-largest-private-credit-pool</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BMO 盈利因拨备高于预期而低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bmo-earnings-miss-estimates-on-higher-than-expected-provisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者和企业难以应对更高的利率，蒙特利尔银行为应对潜在信贷损失拨备了比预期更多的资金，因此该银行的业绩不及分析师预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bmo-earnings-miss-estimates-on-higher-than-expected-provisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团拒绝必和必拓延长报价期限的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/anglo-rejects-bhp-s-request-to-extend-offer-deadline-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 不会再给必和必拓集团 (BHP Group) 任何时间来承诺收购要约，这标志着两大矿业巨头之间长达五周的争斗达到了高潮，此时距离必和必拓承诺收购要约的最后期限仅剩几个小时。威尔·肯尼迪 (Will Kennedy) 在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-29/anglo-rejects-bhp-s-request-to-extend-offer-deadline-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:08:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票结束前几天，印度赢得标普评级展望提升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/s-p-raises-india-s-rating-outlook-to-positive-on-strong-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级表示，未来几个月印度的主权信用评级可能会上调，这将在选举结果公布前不到一周给总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政府带来提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/s-p-raises-india-s-rating-outlook-to-positive-on-strong-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 08:04:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
